Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:04.23,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Wide Heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:11.99,Default,BERG,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving us, Lady Schnee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:16.44,Default,BERG,0,0,0,,We were just thinking \Nwe'd be forced to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:17.12,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:22.05,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I was only able to defeat it \Nbecause you and your men fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:25.75,Default,BERG,0,0,0,,You honor us with such praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:28.28,Italics,BERG,0,0,0,,For the past month,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:32.76,Italics,BERG,0,0,0,,undead that shouldn't be able to leave the \NGhost Plains have been showing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:36.26,Italics,BERG,0,0,0,,We've dispatched elite units\N to take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:41.64,Italics,BERG,0,0,0,,I can't believe she took down a monster alone\N that we've failed to defeat in groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:46.29,Italics,BERG,0,0,0,,I should have expected as much from someone\Nwho once earned a high human's favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:51.53,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,That was the last of the irregular monsters \Nmentioned in your report, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.90,Default,BERG,0,0,0,,Yes. I hope that's the end of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:00:57.89,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I'll continue searching the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:02.64,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,If anything happens, \Nlaunch that magic item I gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:03.41,Default,BERG,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:04.66,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:11.33,Flashback,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.14,0:01:15.91,Italics,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I finally get to see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:54.15,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Wil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:08.70,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there. Finish it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.16,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:13.90,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:20.37,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Wh-What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.28,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Lacia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.18,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:26.59,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,This effect occurs when you meet\Nthe conditions to learn a new skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:30.82,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Hey, Lacia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:31.31,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:35.54,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,You look lost in thought. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.02,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.69,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,My mind was suddenly flooded with \Nimages of how to use the skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:45.57,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Well, in any event,\N you've successfully learned Purify.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:47.00,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.45,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.69,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.83,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Now we'll be able to save the orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:57.84,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,After a short break, let's leave \Nthe sealed area and return to Bayrelicht.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.59,Default,WILHILM,0,0,0,,Yeah. No reason to stick around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.19,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.51,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.09,Default,WILHILM,0,0,0,,Hey, what are... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:15.93,Default,WILHILM,0,0,0,,The hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.74,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,It's pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.62,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,That's the magic matter\N that animates undead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.36,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Magic matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:30.89,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Yeah. Drain it from monsters until they\N can't maintain their form, and they vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.27,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs12\shad0\bord0\b1\c&HDCEAEC&\pos(517.714,225.047)}Skullface Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:51.27,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs10\shad0\bord0\b1\c&HE3E0F3&\pos(400.476,228.667)}Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:51.27,Main - Top,SHIN,0,0,0,,Level 804?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:54.27,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,What an unbelievable monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.52,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:59.52,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,A creature of that level could \Ndestroy an entire nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:03.78,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,We have the seal. W-We'll be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.86,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:24.70,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,So much for the seal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.94,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Yeah. That blow would've shattered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.77,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.84,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Hey, it's looking our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:41.69,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.83,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:50.29,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Not gonna let us escape, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.20,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:01.05,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Wil, what should we do? Hey, Wil!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:03.75,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Keep it together.\NShouting won't help anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:07.18,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,C'mon, Shin! Let's break\N through them and flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.84,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,No. I'm staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.80,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,What? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.01,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,You got a death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:14.77,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Limit Off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:20.40,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Now that the seal is gone, \NI can't allow these monsters to roam free.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:25.14,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'll stop them here and now\N before they cause more damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:26.90,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You two make a break for the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.10,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,This power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:30.91,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.41,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Take care of Yuzuha and Lacia for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.84,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,You've got some explaining \Nto do once we're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:38.57,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:41.58,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'll cast a physical enhancement buff on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.93,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You'll run faster than normal, so don't trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.42,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:48.58,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Hey. The fox won't let go of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.47,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow! Come on, Yuzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:57.17,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Fine. You'd better not leave my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.49,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Looks like you reached an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:02.94,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll clear the way for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.85,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Lightning Banker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.14,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.08,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,They're off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.33,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Let's get started, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:29.93,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Fox Fire, huh? Nice one, Yuzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.60,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,If this happens every time it roars,\Nwe'll be here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:41.10,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yuzuha, this is gonna get a little wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.79,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.11,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Flying Sparrow Thunder Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.37,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That took out a decent number of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:01.63,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Ugh, the map is solid red.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:05.88,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,If only Schnee were here, \NI'd have more options for fighting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:07.89,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,A blue marker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:10.72,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Blue is for allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:13.93,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,But wait. If it's getting closer, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:17.58,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yuzuha, we're gonna make a quick detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:39.42,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,H-How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:45.04,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Read the room, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:48.79,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yuzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.19,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,A barrier, huh? Thanks, Yuzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:58.80,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Schnee—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.81,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,S-Schnee?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:10.19,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Don't you have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:15.61,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Um, sorry for abandoning you all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.65,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:21.60,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks for watching over the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.70,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:25.70,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,She doesn't want an apology or thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.58,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,What does that leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:31.21,Default,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,940)\fnTimes New Roman\b1\fs8\t(\fs10)\shad0\move(320.333,217.333,320.333,225.333)\c&H99A3C3&\3c&H394257&}Moon Sanctum
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:30.11,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,What haven't I said yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.71,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,What should I be saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.61,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:39.97,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.30,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:49.90,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I thought you'd never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:51.48,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:55.30,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Ending the death game\Nshould have wiped my save data,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:58.74,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,including the Moon Sanctum, Schnee, \Nand my other followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:01.24,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yuzuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:03.99,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,The barrier wore off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:12.54,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We've got a lot to discuss, \Nbut why don't we deal with this first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:13.75,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:16.80,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I figured we can fire off one huge attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:17.90,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,A good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.49,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,We've got just the thing for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:24.71,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:28.92,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's been a while \Nsince we last worked together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:29.90,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,It has.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:33.65,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That which is pure, reveal yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:37.15,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,That which is eternal, reveal yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:38.90,Default,BOTH,0,0,0,,Sanctuary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.74,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:18.94,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:24.95,Default,LORD,0,0,0,,Give... that power... to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:30.14,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Did this thing... just talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:33.54,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Master, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.84,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine. All good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:39.84,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,In the end, I didn't learn anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:43.29,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Feels like I should have been able to, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:45.58,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Guess that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:46.85,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,It certainly seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:51.64,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,This place will return \Nto how it once was eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:55.86,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Since we're here, we don't we chat a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:58.49,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:05.36,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Do you remember sending me off \Nwhen I went to defeat Origin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:06.37,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:11.12,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Well, I slew him, which should've\N put an end to everything.
