Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:14.37,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,But there were these huge doors\Nin the dungeon boss room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.14,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,And when I beat the boss, they opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:20.46,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Doors, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:25.65,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah. Then I lost consciousness\Nand woke up in a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:28.89,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,So it's not like I just \Nwandered off for 500 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:32.05,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I see. So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:32.94,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Schnee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.40,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:40.19,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,The dungeon disappeared without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:46.21,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,When other players' support characters \Nstarted saying their masters had vanished,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:49.35,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I knew you'd cleared the dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:54.05,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,But we found it strange that we remained\Nwhen we should've disappeared with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:55.98,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,so we decided to look for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:13:02.80,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,However, seismic shifts \Nthrew the continent into chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:06.30,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,so we split up to work separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:10.21,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I returned to the Moon Sanctum, \Nwhich brings us to the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:14.31,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,That more or less lines up with my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:17.06,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Master, is there something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:19.19,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,No. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:22.49,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,By the way, Schnee...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:26.70,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Could you stop calling me "Master"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:30.13,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,What's wrong with calling my master "Master"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:36.96,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It would cause a fuss if someone overheard\Na legend like you addressing me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.71,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I see. Then how shall I address you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:44.18,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Huh? Can't you just call me by my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:45.47,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I-I daren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.17,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Schnee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.97,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,W-Well, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:54.22,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.23,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:58.22,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I thought my heart would give out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.48,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.48,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing. Really, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.74,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Anyway, call me Shin from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.74,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Very well, Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:10.42,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:14.89,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Shin, what are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:19.45,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Well, first I'm thinking of visiting \Nthe sacred site I read about
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.75,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,in my research at the kingdom's library.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:23.52,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Ever been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:27.93,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Yes. Only for a cursory \Ninvestigation, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:30.94,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I don't know what it's like on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.01,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:35.62,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Then I'll have to go check it out myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.47,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,If you find a way to leave this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:42.86,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,will you return home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.26,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.39,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:56.65,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Of course you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.30,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:01.79,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,It's all right. I figured you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.79,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Say, Schnee...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:09.49,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,How much do you remember from the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:10.93,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:12.43,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:16.97,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Everything from the day \Nwe descended to this land together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:19.87,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I remember it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.19,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Don't bother telling me to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.44,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:32.82,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I became more aware during the period \Nyou and the others called the death game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:36.95,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Until then, it was like I'd been\N watching a video
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:40.14,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,or observing the situation from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.39,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:49.46,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,In other words, they knew \Nthey'd disappear after we logged out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:54.47,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,When I think about what you guys \Nmust've been going through then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:58.31,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,If we'd said anything, \Nit only would have troubled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:01.65,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,It was the right choice at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:02.65,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:07.99,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,We weren't completely autonomous then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:10.42,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,so either way, we couldn't have done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:15.99,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Even so, you can't expect me not to second\Nguess it now that I know you were self-aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:19.50,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,You're as difficult as ever, Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.37,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Shut up. Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:27.89,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,But even if you'd known, \Nyou still would have gone to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:29.69,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:33.17,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Besides, we made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:37.82,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:46.65,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:49.66,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,That's enough solemn talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:51.57,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Let's not spoil our reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:54.78,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Right? Let's party once we're back \Nat the Moon Sanctum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.26,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Yes, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:17:00.51,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,But first, I'd like to ask you something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:05.93,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:06.67,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:10.05,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,It's a long story, but we're partners now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:12.00,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Meet Yuzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:14.42,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Between you and me, Yuzuha's an Elementail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:16.18,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,An Elementail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:19.80,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I knew it was no ordinary spirit \Nwhen I saw those tails, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:21.80,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You could tell by the tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:24.73,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Have you not noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.82,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,There are three...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.20,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Good morning, Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:37.88,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,What?! Wait a minute, Yuzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:40.01,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You can talk now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:45.19,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,My head cleared up \Nwhen that black stuff disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:46.46,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Black stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:51.54,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, the shrine \Nwas surrounded by Skullfaces, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:54.78,Italics,SHIN,0,0,0,,That Lord must've been their leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:58.14,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,In any case, no speaking in front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:59.45,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Aw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:01.55,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Normal spirit foxes don't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:05.58,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Then can I speak inside your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.06,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You mean telepathy? That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:11.61,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,But Shin, now that it has more tails,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.69,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,you can't pass it off as a Little Fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:16.90,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yuzuha, can you merge your tails into one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:17.95,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.70,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.86,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Can you do this when we're around people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:28.76,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:30.46,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Well, that was an easy solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.34,Default,YUZUHA,0,0,0,,Was I good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.21,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Yes, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.47,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.47,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.31,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Wanna pet it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:44.85,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:50.10,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,You always find ways to surprise me, Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:56.54,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,No one has ever successfully \Ntamed an Elementail before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:58.92,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You seem pretty calm in spite of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:02.74,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,I was surprised, but I figured \Nyou of all people could pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:07.28,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Unlike the one we fought previously, \Nthis one isn't high-level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:10.75,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Pulling your punches to weaken one\Nwould would be no easy feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.98,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Normally, you can't let your \Nguard down around their kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.98,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:19.76,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:22.61,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I sent my companions\N back without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:24.34,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,Then we should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:26.01,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,We may be able to catch up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:28.90,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,You're right. We'll go as quick as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.08,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Don't want anyone reporting this to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:35.37,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,If you'd told me that sooner, \Nwe could have saved our talk for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:41.42,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,I couldn't wait after seeing your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.54,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,This and that are entirely separate matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:47.97,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:48.77,Default,SCHNEE,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:58.63,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Hey, Wil. Shin will be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:02.18,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You know how strong he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.26,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:07.49,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Something's coming. At a crazy-fast speed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:08.14,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Wil...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:08.89,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.77,Default,LACIA,0,0,0,,Did that monster follow us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:13.52,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,It's coming in hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.56,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,We'll engage it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.78,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Hey, Wilhelm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:26.11,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Looks like we caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:28.45,Default,SHIN,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:33.98,Default,WILHELM,0,0,0,,Don't confuse me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:39.01,Default,ALDI,0,0,0,,Look at the ground here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.38,Default,KNIGHT 4,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:43.11,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Have you learned anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:46.84,Default,ALDI,0,0,0,,No. I'm sorry, Lady Rionne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:47.93,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:53.39,Italics,RIONNE,0,0,0,,After we heard that mysterious voice, \Na horde of Skullfaces suddenly appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.13,Italics,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Then that light filled the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:21:01.15,Italics,RIONNE,0,0,0,,The Skullfaces turned to dust, \Nand we were all healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:03.31,Italics,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Who could've been responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:09.41,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,Forgive me for interrupting you, \Nbut could you take a look at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:10.86,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:13.91,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,It was on the ground \Nat the far end of the fissure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:18.67,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,It was jammed at the starting point, \Nso I believe this sword was the origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:22.21,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,I don't know what kind of skill \Ndid it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.44,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:24.91,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:27.80,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,What do you see on this sword here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:30.56,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Some kind of bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.94,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,Yes. I believe it's what's known as a falcon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:37.65,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,I know a blacksmith \Nwho carves these on their swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.81,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,Watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:41.89,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:45.82,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,Not only did it not break, \Nbut it's still this powerful, even nicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.94,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,As far as I'm aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:50.90,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,there's only one smith \Nwho forges swords this fine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:53.58,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,and engraves their work with falcons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:55.83,Default,RIONNE,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:57.33,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,A high human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:04.02,Default,GADRAS,0,0,0,,The Black Blacksmith, the most \Nskilled smithy of his kind.
